OL,3,CBritish-Israeli hostage reunited with
OL,4,Cfriends after 15 months in captivity
OL,6,FIt's an image that's quickly become
OL,7,Ficonic in Israel. Emily Damari, the
OL,8,FBritish-Israeli hostage freed this
OL,9,Fweek, holding up a bandaged hand,
OL,10,Fhaving lost two of her fingers but not
OL,11,Fan ounce of her spirit.
OL,13,FThe 28-year-old was handed over by
OL,14,FHamas to the Red Cross in chaotic
OL,15,Fscenes in Gaza.
OL,17,FBut despite an unthinkable 15 months
OL,18,Fin captivity, when the cameras
OL,19,Fcaptured a quick glimpse of Emily, she
OL,20,Fwas smiling.
