OL,6,FIt was the last thing many observers,
OL,7,Ffearing the worst about her condition,
OL,8,Fexpected to see. But those closest to
OL,9,Fher weren't in the least bit surprised.
OL,11,FI met Liki and Guy, who grew up with
OL,12,FEmily on the Kibbutz she was dragged
OL,13,Ffrom on October 7, outside the Tel
OL,14,FAviv hospital where she is staying.
OL,16,F"We knew that she had been through
OL,17,Fhell," Guy told me.
