OL,3,CBritish-Israeli hostage reunited with
OL,4,Cfriends after 15 months in captivity
OL,6,F"She'd been in tunnels and apartments
OL,7,Fback in Gaza. But to see her for a
OL,8,Fsecond, when they managed to capture a
OL,9,Fpicture of her and she was smiling was
OL,10,Famazing. We knew we are getting back
OL,11,Four Emily, the Emily that we know. It
OL,12,Fwas awesome."
OL,14,FWhen Emily was re-united with her mum,
OL,15,FMandy, her friends were waiting as the
OL,16,Fhelicopter carrying her to the
OL,17,Fhospital landed.
