OL,3,CBritish-Israeli hostage reunited with
OL,4,Cfriends after 15 months in captivity
OL,6,F"We managed to hold her hand when she
OL,7,Flanded in the helicopter. She saw us
OL,8,Fand she shouted at the driver to stop.
OL,9,FIt was so important for her to stop
OL,10,Ffor even a second. And then inside the
OL,11,Fhospital we could hold her, kiss her
OL,12,Fon her cheek and tell her how much we
OL,13,Flove her."
OL,15,FHaving spent a few hours with her,
OL,16,FLiki can't stop smiling. She tells me
OL,17,Fhow Emily can now speak Arabic as well
OL,18,Fas she speaks Hebrew and how relieved
OL,19,Fshe was that her super-sociable friend
OL,20,Fwasn't held alone, but alongside
OL,21,Ffellow hostage Romi Goren.
