OL,6,FBoth friends laugh when I ask them
OL,7,Fwhat Emily missed most, after her
OL,8,Ffriends and family. "Food, meat, maybe
OL,9,Fsome alcohol and good music...
OL,10,Fpartying with her friends," said Guy.
