OL,6,FBoth of them are only too aware of the
OL,7,Fhostages that haven't returned. A
OL,8,Fnumber of them come from their
OL,9,Fkibbutz, including Emily's friend Gali
OL,10,Fwho was with her when she was taken,
OL,11,Fand his twin brother Ziv.
OL,13,FEmily's hand, shot as she was taken,
OL,14,Fwas tended in captivity by Romi, who
OL,15,Ftrained as a medic. Liki adopts the
OL,16,Fgesture Emily made shortly after her
OL,17,Frelease in a selfie with her mother,
OL,18,Fholding out her thumb and her little
OL,19,Ffinger.
